        <mxCell id="p2-body" value="Playwright (headless)&#xa;Zawya detail pages&#xa;innerText parsing&#xa;&#xa;Output (SPARSE):&#xa;• description&#xa;• website, founded_year&#xa;• address, phone, email&#xa;• employees_count&#xa;&#xa;Storage:&#xa;→ Supabase companies table&#xa;&#xa;Status: COMPLETE&#xa;Note: Data is very&#xa;inconsistent/missing" style="text;html=0;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=5;" vertex="1" parent="p2">
