          <mxGeometry x="0" y="0" width="280" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="p3-body" value="7-Stage Pipeline:&#xa;1. Init company_details row&#xa;2. Web search (Google/Bing, 10-12 queries)&#xa;3. Website scrape (Playwright)&#xa;4. LLM profile extraction (1-2 calls)&#xa;5. Profile complete (validation)&#xa;6. Scoring (YAML config per sector)&#xa;7. Vectorize (Pinecone)&#xa;&#xa;Output:&#xa;• Rich company profile (20+ fields)&#xa;• sector_metadata JSONB&#xa;• 4 dimension scores (0-10)&#xa;• base_score (0-100)&#xa;• Evidence + confidence per dimension&#xa;• 1536-dim vector embeddings&#xa;&#xa;Storage:&#xa;→ Supabase company_details&#xa;→ Supabase company_scores&#xa;→ Pinecone hak-company-profiles&#xa;&#xa;Scope:&#xa;• Multi-sector UAE (all 30 sectors)&#xa;• YAML scoring configs per sector&#xa;• Decoupled: profile ≠ scoring&#xa;• LLM-agnostic (Claude / OpenAI)&#xa;&#xa;Status: IN PROGRESS" style="text;html=0;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=5;" vertex="1" parent="p3">
          <mxGeometry x="0" y="35" width="280" height="560" as="geometry" />
